“””
DVSA Practical Test Slot Checker
─────────────────────────────────
Polls the DVSA booking system for available test slots at Cheltenham
between 1 May 2026 and 1 August 2026.

Notifications: Gmail email + ntfy.sh push notification (phone/desktop).
Designed to run as a scheduled GitHub Actions job every 15 minutes.
“””

